{"ID":270371, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"371\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs370.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs372.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 371<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">through all.<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> But if Joseph Smith says there are Gods many and Lords many,<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> they cry, &ldquo;Away with\n  him! Crucify him! Crucify him!&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Mankind verily say that the Scriptures are with them.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> Search the Scriptures,<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> for they testify\n  of things that these apostates would gravely pronounce blasphemy.<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> Paul, if Joseph Smith is a\n  blasphemer, you are. I say there are Gods many and Lords many, but to us only one,<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> and we are to\n  be in subjection to that one,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> and no man can limit the bounds or the eternal existence of eternal\n  time.<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> Hath he beheld the eternal world,<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> and is he authorized to say that there is only one God?<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span>\n  He makes himself a fool if he thinks or says so, and there is an end of his career or progress in\n  knowledge. He cannot obtain all knowledge, for he has sealed up the gate to it.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Scriptural Interpretation<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">Some say I do not interpret the Scripture<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> the same as they do. They say it means the heathen&rsquo;s\n  gods.<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> Paul says there are Gods many and Lords many;<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> and that makes a plurality of Gods, in spite\n  of the whims of all men. Without a revelation, I am not going to give them the knowledge of the God\n  of heaven.<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> You know and I testify that Paul had no allusion to the heathen gods.<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> I have it from\n  God, and get over it if you can. I have a witness of the Holy Ghost,<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> and a testimony that Paul had\n  no allusion to the heathen gods in the text. I will show from the Hebrew Bible that I am correct, and\n  the first word<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> shows a plurality of Gods; and I want the apostates and learned men to come here\n  and prove to the contrary, if they can. An unlearned boy must give you a little Hebrew. <i>Berosheit<\/i>\n  <i>baurau Eloheim ait aushamayeen vehau auraits,<\/i> rendered by King James&rsquo; translators, &ldquo;In the\n  beginning God created the heaven and the earth.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> I want to analyze the word <i>Berosheit. Rosh,<\/i> the\n  head; <i>Sheit,<\/i> a grammatical termination; the <i>Baith<\/i> was not originally put there when the inspired man\n  wrote it, but it has been since added by an old Jew. <i>Baurau<\/i> signifies to bring forth; <i>Eloheim<\/i> is from\n  the word <i>Eloi,<\/i><span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span> God, in the singular number; and by adding the word <i>heim,<\/i> it renders it Gods. It read\n  first, &ldquo;In the beginning the head of the Gods brought forth the Gods,&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">21<\/span> or, as others have translated\n  it, &ldquo;The head of the Gods called the Gods together.&rdquo;  I want to show a little learning as well as other\n  fools.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"wideEllipse\">* * *<\/p>\n\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109801\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109801)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109801)\">Eph. 4:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114207\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114207)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114207)\">D&amp;C 63:59<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114800\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114800)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114800)\">D&amp;C 88:6,41<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109474\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109474)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109474)\">1 Cor. 8:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108595\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108595)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108595)\">Luke 23:18,21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108884\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108884)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108884)\">John 19:6,15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109185\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109185)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109185)\">Acts 21:36<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108549\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108549)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108549)\">Luke 16:29,31<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108563\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108563)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108563)\">Luke 20:28<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108690\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108690)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108690)\">John 5:45-46<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108707\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108707)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108707)\">John 7:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108689\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108689)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108689)\">John 5:39<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107909\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107909)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107909)\">Matt. 9:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108267\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108267)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108267)\">Matt. 26:65<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108756\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108756)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108756)\">John 10:33,36<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109478\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109478)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109478)\">1 Cor. 8:5-6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110135\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110135)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110135)\">Heb. 2:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110306\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110306)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110306)\">Heb. 12:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112264\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112264)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112264)\">Alma 40:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114477\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114477)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114477)\">D&amp;C 76:86<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116729\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116729)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116729)\">Moses 1:20<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110535\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110535)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110535)\">2 Pet. 1:20<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116976\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116976)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116976)\">Abr. 1:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109475\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109475)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109475)\">1 Cor. 8:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107956\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107956)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107956)\">Matt. 11:27<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109479\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109479)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109479)\">1 Cor. 8:5-6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109321\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109321)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109321)\">Rom. 9:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113242\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113242)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113242)\">D&amp;C 14:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"105949\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 105949)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(105949)\">Gen. 1:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"105950\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 105950)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(105950)\">Gen. 1:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108371\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108371)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108371)\">Mark 15:34<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"105951\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 105951)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(105951)\">Gen. 1:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}